Description:
Click this to exit
Acthouggas was a normal person, until he met
Michael, he also studied the Dark Arts,
but unlike Michael, he didnt get caught,
he then decided to become an amalgam,
join the rebel forces, and take on the name
Acthouggas. he was a valuable asset to the rebels as he was
able to free Manachrei, he is running
from the facility currently and is great
friends with Manachrei, he also has
magical body markings for some reason, and is
related to Johnathan, in some way we
cant exactly understand very well.
